"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-03-olympics-2024-mens-football-semi-final-fixtures-date-time-confirmed\", \"text\": \"Published  on  By  The semi-final fixtures, date and time for the Paris 2024 Olympic Men's football event have been confirmed.  This follows the conclusion of Friday's quarter-final stage matches.  Recall that Egypt defeated Paraguay 5-4 on penalties after the match ended 1-1, while France won 1-0 against Argentina.  Spain won 3-0 against Japan and Morocco defeated USA 4-0.  Olympics Men's semi-final fixtures:  Morocco vs Spain (Monday - 5pm)  France vs Egypt (Monday - 8pm).  Transfer: Maresca breaks silence after banning Chelsea player from dressing room  EPL: Ten Hag reveals Man Utd star will return to squad in two months  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\"}"